Some notable accomplishments and policies associated with Joe Biden include:

* Authoring the Violence Against Women Act (1994)
* Supporting LGBTQ+ rights and same-sex marriage equality (2012)
* Playing a key role in passing the Affordable Care Act (Obamacare) during the Obama administration (2010)
* Proposing various climate change initiatives, including rejoining the Paris Agreement (2020)
* Advocating for increased investment in infrastructure, education, and healthcare

Throughout his career, Biden has been known for his folksy, down-to-earth demeanor and his ability to connect with everyday Americans.
